data.description: Welcome to Paradise Ridge, where the perfect fusion of opulence and spaciousness awaits you. This extraordinary residence is a true testament to luxury living, featuring immaculately manicured grounds, a refined interior, and breathtaking panoramic views. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an awe-inspiring two-story foyer and an expansive formal dining room, setting the stage for elegant entertaining. The kitchen, a culinary enthusiast's dream, boasts sleek granite countertops, double ovens, and an abundance of storage space within the plentiful cabinets. Picture yourself indulging in quiet moments by the stylish double-sided fireplace, nestled between the inviting living room and the well-appointed kitchen. The main level plays host to the master suite, where walk-in closets, a spa-like tub, and a walk-in shower await, providing the ultimate retreat. Ascending to the upper level, you'll discover a newly adorned living area adorned with stunning new flooring, leaving a lasting impression. The fully finished basement offers endless possibilities, accommodating either a self-contained apartment or a comfortable in-law suite. Embrace the opportunity to discover your own personal sanctuary within this idyllic slice of paradise. Don't miss the chance to experience this exceptional property, previously featured on the esteemed Dalton Tour of Lights.
